<p itemprop="description">A lead enterprise architect provides visionary leadership for enterprise architecture across the organisation. They shape digital strategy, lead major transformation initiatives, and build world-class enterprise architecture capabilities.</p>

<section class="role-details">
    <h2>Typical responsibilities</h2>
    <ul>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Define and execute organisation-wide digital transformation strategy</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Lead major enterprise architecture programmes across multiple departments</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Build and lead high-performing enterprise architecture teams</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Influence C-level executives on technology strategy and investment</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Establish enterprise architecture practice and governance frameworks</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Drive innovation and adoption of emerging technologies</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Represent the organisation in external architecture forums</li>
    </ul>
</section>

